General.Name: Surefire Resources NL
General.Description: Surefire Resources NL explores for and reviews mineral tenement holdings in Western Australia. It explores for gold, copper, lead, silver, vanadium, and iron ore deposits. The company was formerly known as Black Ridge Mining NL and changed its name to Surefire Resources NL in December 2016. Surefire Resources NL was incorporated in 1998 and is based in South Perth, Australia.
